snippet.title: Game Boy | Hook (Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Name: Hook
Developer: Ocean Software
Platform: Game Boy
Year: 1992
Genre: Platformer

A game where you have no clue what to do where you reach the end of the level and have to backtrack a million times to find certain pick-ups in which feels like a maze.
